Subject: Need new installation media and support for setup on new system.
Description: We are prepared to move all of our seats to a new server but no longer have a current iso for the EPP environment, nor access to the old system that is no longer in use.
What_We_Know__c: We have asked for a new license file containing all 300 endpoints that have been divided between 2 servers, and now need to be all on the same new server.
Solution_Comment__c: We have helped the customer with the download links for the EPP Server image, and also provided the requested license file.
